{"tid":771972,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【中美貿易戰】中方拋售美債「攬炒」？ 德媒：最大損失係自己","createTime":"2018-08-08T11:32:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-09T01:16:10.000Z","uid":150685,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"8b2c242f19e573d01b7e55765b40ee5df809fbb2","tid":771972,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T11:32:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180808/large/1533699029_ad9b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180808%2Flarge%2F1533699029_ad9b.jpg&h=d58aba66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中美貿易戰越演越烈，美國貿易代表周二表示，將在本月23日開始向160億美元（約1,248億港元）中國貨徵收關稅。兩國互不相讓下，有指中國尚有一道撒手鐧，就是拋售數以萬億計的美國國債，讓本來債台高築的美國政府陷入被動。但德國《新蘇黎世報》報道，拋售美國國債，對中國來說並不是一個理想的選擇。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，如果中國拋售美國國債，最終損失最大的將是中國自己。因為，中國一旦大量拋售美國國債，債券價格就會下跌。中國不可能一次過拋售所有美債，只能在最短一年半時間內分期分批出售，每次拋售相當數量的美債，都會導致剩餘債券的貶值，即是對中國來說，拋售美債將是一個賠本買賣。<br />\n<br />\n報道又提出，即便中國政府拋售美債，處理收回的巨額美元現金也成一個棘手問題。如果用美金購買其他貨幣，吃虧的仍是中國。<br />\n<br />\n商業銀行分析師威登施泰內爾（Bernd Weidensteiner）認為，中國如果大量拋售美元，將導致美元貶值，人民幣則會升值，讓中國出口產品價格升高。由於美國增收關稅已抬高中國產品價格，故中國領導人顯然不希望國產貨品價格再進一步被提升。中國領導人或可用美元購買美國股票或企業，但鑑於目前的中美關係，美國政界必不會同意中方大規模收購美國公司。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180808/58537083\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180808%2F58537083&d=y8y8TxoB%2BWH7vemxOF3vhU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=b0e1b04f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180808%2F58537083&h=fff1d94f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180808/58537083</a>"},{"pid":"1a582cab190683dd9a368ca3c3f25f118f656e07","tid":771972,"uid":23180,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T11:39:03.000Z","msg":"危言聳聽<br />\n<br />\n贏國應馬上亮劍拋售所有美債"},{"pid":"a233725927e18f21df9fa5a10d08646618464aaa","tid":771972,"uid":141151,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"1a582cab190683dd9a368ca3c3f25f118f656e07","tid":771972,"uid":23180,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T11:39:03.000Z","msg":"危言聳聽<br />\n<br />\n贏國應馬上亮劍拋售所有美債"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T11:42:29.000Z","msg":"冇錯<br />\n寶劍出鞘啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1288b8ec5af75275f90d7f1d0a92d9a459a8ba6a","tid":771972,"uid":35430,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T15:47:20.000Z","msg":"拋啦拋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一堆人準備入美債<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad89fff6aa1f9fcd27a90ff92f00159bd472057d","tid":771972,"uid":56219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T15:52:40.000Z","msg":"亮劍 亮劍 唔拋正廢柴"},{"pid":"f3fbb9bd0cf8a8d4f3dca241ed01fc7670036a9a","tid":771972,"uid":56123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a233725927e18f21df9fa5a10d08646618464aaa","tid":771972,"uid":141151,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"1a582cab190683dd9a368ca3c3f25f118f656e07","tid":771972,"uid":23180,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T11:39:03.000Z","msg":"危言聳聽<br />\n<br />\n贏國應馬上亮劍拋售所有美債"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T11:42:29.000Z","msg":"冇錯<br />\n寶劍出鞘啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T16:45:35.000Z","msg":"支持，美帝破壞我地2025計畫，一定要還擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbf8081245fbc03a32e5b0a23ee73a8201a2ada1","tid":771972,"uid":104699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T16:49:38.000Z","msg":"搬石砸腳"},{"pid":"ac4f0b3c7f088df308e7cb1b2499335ba46296a6","tid":771972,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T00:17:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkg